dct_title_s: Outline map of Paris, France : showing principal places of interest
dct_description_sm: In upper margin: If you go to the Paris Exposition you will find this map a great convenience. Includes advertisements for wood products manufactured by John W. Boughton. Includes calendars for 1900 and 1901. Map on side 2 has title: Map of London, England.
dct_publisher_sm: Philadelphia : Published by John W. Boughton ... , [1900?]
